In the event of EE-00059-1's reemergence upon contact with the location, the Altruist-9's support structures and core payload[[footnote]] Containing a small, solar-powered autonomous drone and atmospheric measuring equipment.[[/footnote]] are kept encased in an exotic polypeptide oligomer weave derived from the wreckage of SCP-001-E1.[[footnote]]See SCP-001 for more information.[[/footnote]] 



[[include <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/component:coltop">:scp-wiki:component:coltop</a>

